      "content": "that's helpful, really strong phrasing for the students. now, to help them prepare for the inevitable counter-arguments, how would a typical opponent argue against these points? like, how would they respond to the rule of law and national security claims? i just want to make sure my kids aren't caught off guard by the common criticisms.",
